===========================================================
===  Instructions for MuonMomentumCorrections-01-00-00  ===
===========================================================

=== News

  - Tool modified to be used with xAODs
   
=== Tool usage examples

  - If you are running in Athena:
    - please look at src/TestMCASTTool.cxx how to use the tool
    - the recommended configurations are loaded by default (no need to set anything on the user's side) 

  - If you are running in RootCore:
    - please look at util/MCAST_Tester.cxx how to use the tool
    - the recommended configurations are the same as the previous case:
      CP::MuonCalibrationAndSmearingTool corrTool( "MuonCorrector" );
      corrTool.initialize();
